          "title": "QUALITY [https://vicuna.lmsys.org/?utm_source=tldrai]",
          "summary": "This paper introduces Vicuna-13B, an open-source chatbot trained by fine-tuning LLaMA on user-shared conversations. Vicuna-13B outperforms other models like LLaMA and Stanford Alpaca in over 90% of cases while achieving a quality of over 90% compared to OpenAI ChatGPT and Google Bard. The cost of training Vicuna-13B is around $300, and the code and demo are publicly available for non-commercial use.",
